snippet.title: Heart. Papers. Border. Pre-Alpha Demo Gameplay
snippet.description:
We take a look at the Pre-Alpha Demo of Heart. Papers. Border., a strategy game about travel, exploration and blogging from Jovian Industries. 

Heart. Papers. Border. on Steam Greenlight: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=862433250

Follow IndieHangover for a new Indiedev interview every week, as well as news, reviews and stories from the world of Indie Game Development.
